library(kableExtra)
tidy(lda, matrix = "beta") %>% 
  group_by(topic) %>% 
  slice_max(beta, n = 15) %>% 
  mutate(term = reorder_within(term, beta, topic)) %>% 
  summarise(term = list(term), .groups = "drop") %>% 
  mutate(
    term = unlist(lapply(term, function(x) paste0(x, collapse = ", ")))
  ) %>% 
  mutate(term = gsub("_", "", term), term = gsub("[0-9]", "", term)) %>% 
  kable() %>% 
  kable_styling()
